Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這麼晚還在外面遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.47,0:01:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  必須得懲罰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.91,0:01:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使不是已經不會傷害我們了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是不會對毫無抵抗的我們進行攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  以半圓形圍住她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行集中攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你這傢伙在發號施令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被distortion擋開  也不要停下攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:26.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.10,0:02:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快閃開  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.23,0:02:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.54,0:02:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼深的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.35,0:03:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是致命傷也會很快好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的傢伙居然有兩個  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界什麼時候變得這麼莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有緣由的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.34,0:03:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得天使領域入侵作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的電腦裡不是有一個開發技能的軟體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面有幾個從未見過的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是其中一個叫「harmonics」的技能發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個什麼樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.57,0:03:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時沒看畫面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把一個身體分裂成兩個的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這也是天使自己用軟體開發的技能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺並非是完全相同的兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙不同  很好戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.25,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她只使用保護自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀刃時也一樣  只是為了擋住子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們這群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為笨蛋基本都聚集在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你們其中一個可能性好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設那個分身的產生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在擁有強烈的攻擊意志的時候的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說分身一直遵從著當時本體的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  奏不可能擁有強烈的攻擊意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這無所謂  不過你好像很護著她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  她很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在的問題是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天使的分身戰鬥的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是消除方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.27,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在幹什麼  快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果分身是因為她的意志而產生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也應該能用她的意志來消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要等她醒來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果能用意志消除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她還會躺在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是無意識下的產物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連她也無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同歸於盡也只好拼命上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不會消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是要一直在這個世界存在下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在放過了我們  但明天開始應該不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦偏離規範行為  恐怕會立刻和昨天一樣變成一場血戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為她完全繼承了約束我們的那份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上生性好戰  糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想反抗也沒有時間去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些時間要怎樣去爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上課  並裝作聽課的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能去聽老師講課的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真上課的話就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被分身發現的情況下幹別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且堅持一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望下次再見的時候  不要少了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:02.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我知道可以分身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法讓另一個消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.51,0:07:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel  Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟體的使用手冊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  這麼厚一本還全是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.66,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是連上這個指令就會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它的發動條件是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把整個電腦都破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎  那分身就不會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  直接改寫成我能明白的程式算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間限制是10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒鐘要等起來還真是漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能設置到10秒以下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.22,0:08:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分身做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪除掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  都做得這麼周密了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡可能少修改一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要她再使用一次「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「absorb」這個技能就會發動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏和我約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過那種約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.28,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副凌亂的樣子肯定是被綁走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改寫了程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她再使用一次那個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加能力就會發動  分身就應該會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣磨槍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵人的行動比預想的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被藏起來的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一邊躲避兇惡的天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是假裝上課就已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻到底能撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼加入GDM的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為崇拜岩澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM可是為了佯攻而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  面對那麼可怕的對手怎麼佯攻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.77,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你佯攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡我可是你的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼反倒是你發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩嗎  真是對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然在演唱會中可能會尿褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份決心先謝謝你了  不過現在還不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.20,0:10:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.74,0:10:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集目擊到天使的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  yo!  Check  this  out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moonwalk, it's a moonwalk... Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛收集來的情報看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁的場所很可能是在Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  一定是在那最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆破掉的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  陷阱也還開啟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最為危險  距離這裡最遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要潛入這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次可幾乎是全滅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一個死的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家我即使尿褲子也會繼續唱下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出自己的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那種對手  佯攻也是等著被秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不需要佯攻  堂堂正正地去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要兼顧和天使的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.27,0:11:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰內容是空降至Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其最底層順利奪回天使的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.88,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的陷阱擱著沒人管  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在這裡碰上天使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會尿褲子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.63,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有手槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.26,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會比預想的更快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是敵人又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  那傢伙又是第一個被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後的要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先對付眼前的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  快沒子彈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去封住路口  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能趕上的人就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.71,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.66,0:13:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:20.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼凶暴的天使居然有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次空降作戰的處境還要糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身都使出「handsonic」和「distortion」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說「harmonics」也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是一群低能兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來總結問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是究竟製造了多少個分身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分身能製造分身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那數量就沒有限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那別說是兩個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十個…二十個  說不定還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由理已經追加過技能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身是會回到本體的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等她們消失不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是第二個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那能力追加以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就已經量產了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民們  終於注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學是高貴的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道我們會潛入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把已經量產了的分身佈置在這個Guild的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後已經有兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聚集了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被困在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連武器也沒法補給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是等著被幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事到底有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言是讓我們完全服從吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們老老實實地消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個把我們一網打盡的絕妙作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.95,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…浪費子彈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  趁我還有意識的時候快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這種好像只有在臨死時才是條好漢的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  趁現在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住啊  松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓松下君白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前進那是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使身體比較小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要封住她的動作的話  那樣做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天使有多麼大的力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的固技對她都會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下君教我們的柔道終於有實用的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對付一個天使只要犧牲一個人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要我們能救出本體  他們也都能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:37.41,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B12
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  my  turn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get  chance  and  luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼啊  這種像少年漫畫最終回一樣的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現這身肌肉的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去意識到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一名小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  在那片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.02,0:17:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個神情很寂寞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你露出笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是壞透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無同學  不是的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是善意的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰來說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我連他名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.90,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  早就沒在數了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的話就給我快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜歡他還是討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild被爆破後的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:36.20,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild最底層  爆炸中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡能一口氣下到最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無君和由依去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到  就催促她使用「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.50,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向君不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她等著的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了  根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請提一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是最後一次作戰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由依呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽到一聲很短暫的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了天使的犧牲品了嗎  太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馬上就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活下來的又只有我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該是最後一個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你別在這裡發呆了  快點去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摀住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.35,0:20:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.78,0:20:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞著耳塞聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  就用另一把匕首割破你的喉嚨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:20:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.29,0:21:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.48,0:21:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線的大家都拼上了性命來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.47,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點勉強你很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望你能使用一個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.31,0:21:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.80,0:21:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你用了大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體能受得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只用一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.93,0:21:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像改寫了程式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  一切都會回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多冷酷的我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.60,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是分身也有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊你們的眾多的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性吸收這麼多的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.31,0:22:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
